#

Mashed Butternut Squash

40 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishComfort FoodFall Recipe

Description

Creamy and naturally sweet mashed butternut squash, perfect as a comforting side dish!

Ingredients

  • butternut squash: 1 medium
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • milk or cream: 1/4 cup
